<meta name="sailthru.title" content="How Shame Over My Psoriasis Led to a Body I’m Proud Of" />
<meta name="sailthru.date" content="2016-04-27T10:30:00-04:00" />
<link href="http://greatist.com/live/how-to-be-confident-my-struggle-with-psoriasis" rel="canonical" />
<script type="application/ld+json">
