  "dateModified": "2016-04-27T13:03:58-04:00",
  "description": "It's about learning to control the things you can to overcome the things you cannot.",
  "about": [
    {
      "@type": "Thing",
      "name": "Live",
      "sameAs": "http://greatist.com/live"
    },
